The paper discusses neural architecture search (NAS), which is a subfield of machine learning and falls under the category of "Learning" (cs.LG) in arXiv. The paper specifically focuses on ensemble learning methods in NAS, which are commonly used in computer vision (cs.CV) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) applications. The proposed method also involves pruning sub-architectures, which is a technique used in neural networks (cs.NE) and control systems (cs.SY). Therefore, the most likely categories are cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.NE, and cs.SY.
